          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-1" n="1">1.<lb/>Here Sarum lyes</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-2" n="2">Of late as wise,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-3" n="3">And Learn'd as Tom Aquinas.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-4" n="4">Lawn-sleeves He wore</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-5" n="5">Yet was no more</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-6" n="6">A Xstian than Socinius.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-7" n="7">2.<lb/>Oaths pro &amp; con</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-8" n="8">He swallowd down</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-9" n="9">Loved gold like any layman</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-10" n="10">Wrote, preachd, &amp; prayd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-11" n="11">And yet betrayd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-12" n="12">Gods Holy Church for Mamon.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-13" n="13">3.<lb/>Of Every Vice</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-14" n="14">He had a Spice</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-15" n="15">Altho a Reverend Prelate.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-16" n="16">Both lived &amp; dyed</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-17" n="17">(Or he's belyed)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-18" n="18">A true dissenting Zealot.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-19" n="19">4.<lb/>If such a Soul</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-20" n="20">To Heaven has stole</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-21" n="21">And 'scaped old Satans clutches</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-22" n="22">We may presume</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-23" n="23">There still is room</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-308B-line-24" n="24">For M──gh &amp; his Dutchess──</l>
          </lg>
